@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yfthit(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.50 / v0 + 0.37)) * wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.79)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.81))
    v1 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.26 * v2 + 0.22) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.71)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.25 - v1 + 0.66)) / (tmp * (v2 + 0.98 / v2 + 0.18)))
    data[tid] = v0
